üéØ CCEE QUICK REVISION (SESSION 7)
Digital Signature = Hash + Private Key
Verification = Public Key
Certificate binds identity ‚Üî public key
CA establishes trust
CRL / OCSP ‚Üí certificate revocation
X.509 = certificate standard
